text: Schwenck is a surname. Notable people with the name include: *Cléber Schwenck Tiene (born 1979, known as Schwenck), Brazilian footballer *Rudy Schwenck (1884-1941), American baseball player *Sir William Schwenck Gilbert (1836-1911), English dramatist and librettist of Gilbert and Sullivan operas *Mary Schwenck (born 1778), aunt of William Gilbert, the librettists's father, and godmother to the librettist ==See also== *, German composer, source of the Schwencke measure *Schwenk *Schwenke (disambiguation) ==References==
